title: Just Work
itunes:title: Just Work
description:
Episode 560 - We all know what we need to do to create the life we want, the issue that we have is how do we just make ourselves do it? That is the only thing holding us back from creating the life of our dreams. In this episode, I will talk about how to turn your brain off and just do the work.
